              "active": true,
              "timeZone": "Asia/Kolkata"
            },
            "body": "Not sure if we need a new executor altogether. I'd think this is very similar to YARN-2161/YARN-1327 for Mac/FreeBSD.",
            "updateAuthor": {
              "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=vinodkv",
